  "bio25": "Lucius P. Thundercat is a Canadian hip-hop rapper and vocalist from Montréal, spanning soulful sample-based hip-hop, boom bap, trap, and lofi across feature-driven collaborative singles. Not affiliated with Thundercat (Stephen Bruner).",
  "bio100": "Lucius P. Thundercat is a Canadian hip-hop rapper and vocalist based in Montréal, releasing through Silk Velvet Records. His music spans soulful sample-based hip-hop, boom bap, trap, and lofi, drawing on dusty vintage soul samples and a melodic R&B-rap crossover. He works feature-first: signature collaborations include \"Must Be Love\" with Magi Merlin and Frei, alongside recurring work with Nick Nigh and Sunnie. His catalog is available across all major streaming platforms and Bandcamp. Not affiliated with Thundercat (Stephen Bruner).",
